| Song                   = [[Ostani kraj mene]]
| Final result           = 15th, 39 points
}}

'''Bosnia and Herzegovina''' participated in the '''Eurovision Song Contest 1994''' in [[Dublin]], Ireland.  [[Alma Čardžić|Alma]] and [[Dejan]] represented Bosnia and Herzegovina with the song "[[Ostani kraj mene]]". They finished in 15th place (highest being a 10 from France) with 39 points. Also this is the only year that Hungary voted for Bosnia and Herzegovina

