==Pequeños Reyes del Aire (2007)== {{Infobox wrestling event |name=''Pequeños Reyes del Aire'' (2007) |image=LuchaLibreObrera017.JPG |caption=[[Pequeño Damián 666]], tournament winner |promotion = [[Consejo Mundial de Lucha Libre]] |date=July 13, 2007 |attendance= |venue=[[Arena Mexico]] |city = [[Mexico City, Mexico]] |liveevent=Y |Torneo Gran Alternativa (2007)|Torneo Gran Alternativa]]'' (2007) |nextevent=[[CMLL 74th Anniversary Show]] |event=''Pequeños Reyes del Aire'' |lastevent2=First |nextevent2=''[[#Pequeños Reyes del Aire (2008)|Pequeños Reyes del Aire]]'' (2008) }} CMLL held their first '''''Pequeños Reyes del Aire''''' tournament in 2007, two years after they created the ''[[CMLL Reyes del Aire|Reyes del Aire]]'' for the regular roster. The match was part of CMLL's regular Friday night show ''[[CMLL Super Viernes]]'' ("Super Friday") on July 13, 2007 as a special attraction match on the under card. The wrestlers had to compete in a 10-man ''[[torneo cibernetico]]'' elimination match to win the ''Pequeños Reyes del Aire'' trophy. In 2005 the match included [[Bam Bam (wrestler)|Bam Bam]], [[Bracito de Oro]], [[Electrico (wrestler)|Eléctrico]], [[Fantasy (Mini-Estrella)|Fantasy]], [[Fire (wrestler)|Fire]], [[Mr. Águilita]], [[Pequeño Damián 666]], [[Pequeño Halloween]], [[Sombrita]] and [[Pequeño Olímpico]] (then reigning [[CMLL World Mini-Estrella Championship|CMLL World Mini-Estrella Champion]]).<ref name=PequenoReyes07/><ref name=SL244/> Pequeño Damián 666 would win the match, eliminating Bam Bam as the last opponent to take the victory.<ref name=SL244/> Four months after his 2007 ''Pequeños Reyes del Aire'' victory Pequeño Damián 666 would defeat Pequeño Olímpico to win the CMLL World Mini-Estrella Championship, although the title match was not a direct prize of the tournament Pequeño Damián 666's victory did elevate him up the contenders ranks.<ref name=SL244>{{cite news|title = 2007 Lo Mejor de la Lucha Mexicana | work =SuperLuchas | id = issue 244 | pages= 16–18 | date = December 26, 2007 | url=http://superluchas.net/?p=1491 | accessdate = July 11, 2009| language = Spanish}}</ref>
;Pequeños Reyes del Aire (2007) order of elimination {| class="wikitable sortable" !style="background: #e3e3e3;"|Order !style="background: #e3e3e3;"|Wrestler !style="background: #e3e3e3;"|Eliminated by |- |{{sort|01|1}} || [[Sombrita]] || [[Bracito de Oro]] |- |{{sort|02|2}} || [[Electrico (wrestler)|Eléctrico]] || [[Mr. Águilita]] |- |{{sort|03|3}} || [[Fire (wrestler)|Fire]] || [[Fantasy (Mini-Estrella)|Fantasy]] |- |{{sort|04|4}} || [[Bracito de Oro]] || [[Pequeño Halloween]] |- |{{sort|05|5}} || [[Mr. Águilita]] || [[Bam Bam (wrestler)|Bam Bam]] |- |{{sort|06|6}} || [[Fantasy (Mini-Estrella)|Fantasy]] || [[Pequeño Damián 666]] |- |{{sort|07|7}} || [[Pequeño Olímpico]] || [[Pequeño Damián 666]] and [[Pequeño Halloween]] |- |{{sort|08|8}} || [[Pequeño Halloween]] || [[Bam Bam (wrestler)|Bam Bam]] |- |{{sort|09|9}} || [[Bam Bam (wrestler)|Bam Bam]] || [[Pequeño Damián 666]] |- |{{sort|10|10}} || [[Pequeño Damián 666]] || '''Winner''' |} {{-}}
==Pequeños Reyes del Aire (2008)== {{Infobox wrestling event |name=''Pequeños Reyes del Aire'' (2008) |image=Tzuki.jpg |caption=[[Tzuki]], only appeared in the 2008 tournament |promotion = [[Consejo Mundial de Lucha Libre]] |date=January 6, 2008 |attendance= |venue=[[Arena Mexico]] |city = [[Mexico City, Mexico]] |liveevent=Y |lastevent=''[[Sin Piedad (2007)|Sin Piedad]]'' (2007) |nextevent=''[[Homenaje a Dos Leyendas (2008)|Homenaje a Dos Leyendas]]'' (2008) |event=''Pequeños Reyes del Aire'' |lastevent2=''[[#Pequeños Reyes del Aire (2007)|Pequeños Reyes del Aire]]'' (2007) |nextevent2=''[[#Pequeños Reyes del Aire (2009)|Pequeños Reyes del Aire]]'' (2009) }} CMLL held their second ever '''''Pequeños Reyes del Aire''''' tournament on January 6, 2008 and like the previous year it was a ''[[torneo cibernetico]]'' elimination match where the last survivor of the match would be crowned that year's ''Pequeño Rey del Aire''.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://superluchas.net/2008/01/03/lucha-libre-en-la-arena-mexico-viernes-4-de-enero-2008/|title=Lucha Libre en la Arena Mexico Viernes 4 de enero 2008|first=Jorge|last=Ocampo|date=January 3, 2008|accessdate=October 15, 2012|work=SuperLuchas|language=Spanish}}</ref> Among the participants was the then reigning [[CMLL World Mini-Estrella Championship|CMLL World Mini-Estrella Champion]] [[Pequeño Damián 666]], who was actually the first man eliminated from the match. Other tournament participants included [[Bam Bam (wrestler)|Bam Bam]], [[Fantasy (Mini-Estrella)|Fantasy]], [[Fire (wrestler)|Fire]], [[Mascarita Dorada]], [[Mr. Águilita]], [[Pequeño Black Warrior]], [[Pequeño Halloween]], [[Shockercito]] and [[Tzuki]]. The winner of the match was Mascarita Dorada, who had only worked for CMLL for a few months at the time and was in the middle of being built up as the focal point of the Mini-Estrellas division.<ref name=PequenoReyes08/><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.mediotiempo.com/mas-deportes/lucha-libre/noticias/2008/01/05/se-impone-wagner-jr-a-ultimo-guerrero | title= Se impone Wagner Jr a Ultimo Guerrero | author= Redaccion MEDIOTIEMP | date= January 5, 2008 | accessdate= October 15, 2012 | work= MedioTiempo | language=Spanish}}</ref>
;Pequeños Reyes del Aire (2008) order of elimination {| class="wikitable sortable" !style="background: #e3e3e3;"|Order !style="background: #e3e3e3;"|Wrestler !style="background: #e3e3e3;"|Eliminated by |- |{{sort|01|1}} || [[Fire (wrestler)|Fire]] || [[Fantasy (Mini-Estrella)|Fantasy]] |- |{{sort|02|2}} || [[Shockercito]] || [[Mr. Águilita]] |- |{{sort|03|3}} || [[Fantasy (Mini-Estrella)|Fantasy]] || [[Pequeño Black Warrior]] |- |{{sort|04|4}} || [[Mr. Águilita]] || [[Bam Bam (wrestler)|Bam Bam]] |- |{{sort|05|5}} || [[Pequeño Black Warrior]] || [[Tzuki]] |- |{{sort|06|6}} || [[Tzuki]] || [[Pequeño Halloween]] |- |{{sort|07|7}} || [[Pequeño Halloween]] || [[Bam Bam (wrestler)|Bam Bam]] |- |{{sort|08|8}} || [[Bam Bam (wrestler)|Bam Bam]] || [[Pequeño Damián 666]] |- |{{sort|09|9}} || [[Pequeño Damián 666]] || [[Mascarita Dorada]] |- |{{sort|10|10}} || [[Mascarita Dorada]] || '''Winner''' |} {{-}}
==Pequeños Reyes del Aire (2009)== {{Infobox wrestling event |name=''Pequeños Reyes del Aire'' (2009) |image= |caption= |promotion = [[Consejo Mundial de Lucha Libre]] |date=January 6, 2009 |attendance= |venue=[[Arena Coliseo]] |city = [[Mexico City, Mexico]] |liveevent=Y |lastevent=''[[Leyenda de Azul#Leyenda de Azul 2008|Leyenda de Azul]]'' (2008) |nextevent=''[[La Hora Cero]]'' |event=''Pequeños Reyes del Aire'' |lastevent2=''[[#Pequeños Reyes del Aire (2008)|Pequeños Reyes del Aire]]'' (2008) |nextevent2=''[[#Pequeños Reyes del Aire (2010)|Pequeños Reyes del Aire]]'' (2010) }} The third annual '''''Pequeños Reyes del Aire''''' tournament took place on Tuesday January 6, 2009 in [[Arena Coliseo]], the first ''Pequeños Reyes del Aire'' tournament to take place outside of [[Arena México]]. The ''torneo cibernetic'' featured nine wrestlers in total, [[Bam Bam (wrestler)|Bam Bam]], [[Mr. Águilita]], [[Niño de Acero]], [[Pequeño Black Warrior]], [[Pequeño Damián 666]], [[Pequeño Halloween]], [[Pequeño Violencia]], [[Toshiya Matsuzaki|Pequeño Ninja]] and [[Último Dragóncito]]. The final of the tournament saw Pequeño Black Warrior pin Último Dragóncito to win the 2009 tournament.<ref name=PequenoReyes09/>
;Pequeños Reyes del Aire (2009) order of elimination {| class="wikitable sortable" !style="background: #e3e3e3;"|Order !style="background: #e3e3e3;"|Wrestler !style="background: #e3e3e3;"|Eliminated by |- |{{sort|01|1}} || [[Mr. Águilita]] || [[Acero (wrestler)|Nino de Acero]] |- |{{sort|02|2}} || [[Bam Bam (wrestler)|Bam Bam]] || [[Pequeño Damián 666]] |- |{{sort|03|3}} || [[Niño de Acero]] || [[Pequeño Halloween]] |- |{{sort|04|4}} || [[Pequeño Damián 666]] || [[Último Dragóncito]] |- |{{sort|05|5}} || [[Pequeño Halloween]] || [[Toshiya Matsuzaki|Pequeño Ninja]] (double pin) |- |{{sort|06|5}} || [[Toshiya Matsuzaki|Pequeño Ninja]] || [[Pequeño Halloween]] (double pin) |- |{{sort|07|7}} || [[Pequeño Violencia]] || [[Mascarita Dorada]] |- |{{sort|08|8}} || [[Último Dragóncito]] || Referee stoppage |- |{{sort|09|9}} || [[Mascarita Dorada]] || [[Pequeño Black Warrior]] |- |{{sort|10|10}} || [[Pequeño Black Warrior]] || '''Winner''' |} {{-}}
==Pequeños Reyes del Aire (2010)== {{Infobox wrestling event |name=''Pequeños Reyes del Aire'' (2010) |image=LuchaLibreObrera005.JPG |caption=[[Shockercito]], one of the 2010 participants |promotion = [[Consejo Mundial de Lucha Libre]] |date=March 7, 2010 |attendance= |venue=[[Arena Coliseo]] |city = [[Mexico City, Mexico]] |liveevent=Y |lastevent=''[[CMLL Torneo Nacional de Parejas Increibles (2010)|Torneo de Parejas Increibles]]'' (2010) |nextevent=''[[Homenaje a Dos Leyendas (2010)|Homenaje a Dos Leyendas]]'' (2010) |event=''Pequeños Reyes del Aire'' |lastevent2=''[[#Pequeños Reyes del Aire (2009)|Pequeños Reyes del Aire]]'' (2009) |nextevent2=''[[#Pequeños Reyes del Aire (2011)|Pequeños Reyes del Aire]]'' (2011) }} The fourth annual '''''Pequeños Reyes del Aire''''' took place on March 7, 2010 in Mexico City, Mexico, during CMLL's ''Domingos de Coliseo'' weekly event in [[Arena Coliseo]].<ref name=PequenoReyes10/> For the first time in the tournament's history [[Pequeño Halloween]] did not participate as he had left CMLL not long before the match. Also absent was the 2008 winner [[Mascarita Dorada]] as well as the holder of the secondary Mini-Estrellas title, the [[Mexican National Lightweight Championship]] [[Pierrothito]], with no explanation of their exclusion.<ref>{{cite web | url= http://www.wrestleview.com/viewnews.php?id=1267767725 | title= Viva La Raza! Lucha Weekly | first= Josh | last=Boutwell | date= March 5, 2010 | accessdate= October 15, 2010 | publisher= WrestleView}}</ref> The match did include the holder of the [[CMLL World Mini-Estrella Championship]] [[Bam Bam (wrestler)|Bam Bam]] and was the first ''Pequeños Reyes del Aire'' tournament for [[Pequeño Nitro]] and [[Pequeño Universo 2000]] and had the repeated appearance of [[Electrico (wrestler)|Eléctrico]], [[Pequeño Black Warrior]], [[Pequeño Damián 666]], [[Pequeño Olímpico]], [[Pequeño Violencia]], [[Shockercito]] and [[Último Dragóncito]] which made for the most participants in the tournament yet.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://superluchas.net/2010/03/06/arena-coliseo-domingo-7-marzo-torneo-de-Pequenos-reyes-del-aire/|title=Arena Coliseo Domingo 7 marzo torneo de Pequenos reyes del aire|first=Alex|last=Ruiz Glez|date=March 7, 2010|accessdate=October 15, 2010|work=SuperLuchas|language=Spanish}}</ref> The tournament was won by relative newcomer Pequeño Nitro who earned a shot at the CMLL World Mini-Estrellas Championship the following week.<ref name=Preyes10>{{cite web|url=http://superluchas.net/2010/03/09/Pequeño-nitro-gana-el-torneo-Pequeños-reyes-del-aire-2010/|title=Pequeño Nitro gana el torneo Pequeños Reyes del Aire 2010|date=March 9, 2010|accessdate=October 15, 2012|work=SuperLuchas|language=Spanish}}</ref> Pequeño Nitro was unsuccessful in his title challenge.
