==Pequeños Reyes del Aire (2011)== {{Infobox wrestling event |name=''Pequeños Reyes del Aire'' (2011) |image= |caption= |promotion = [[Consejo Mundial de Lucha Libre]] |date=February 5, 2011 |attendance= |venue=[[Arena Coliseo]] |city = [[Mexico City, Mexico]] |liveevent=Y |lastevent=[[Fantastica Mania 2011]] |nextevent=''[[CMLL Torneo Nacional de Parejas Increibles (2011)|CMLL Torneo de Parejas Increibles]]'' (2010) |event=''Pequeños Reyes del Aire'' |lastevent2=''[[#Pequeños Reyes del Aire (2010)|Pequeños Reyes del Aire]]'' (2010) |nextevent2=''[[#Pequeños Reyes del Aire (2012)|Pequeños Reyes del Aire]]'' (2012 Mexico City) }} CMLL held their annual '''''Pequeños Reyes del Aire''''' tournament on February 6, 2011 although they promoted the fact that the winner would get a shot at the [[CMLL World Mini-Estrella Championship]] than the tournament aspects of it. The 10 man ''[[torneo cibernetico]]'' saw the ''[[Face (professional wrestling)|tecnicos]]'' ("good guys") team of [[Astral (wrestler)|Astral]], [[Electrico (wrestler)|Eléctrico]], [[Fantasy (Mini-Estrella)|Fantasy]], [[Mascarita Dorada]] and [[Mini Maximo]] faced off against the ''[[Heel (professional wrestling)|rudos]]'' ("bad guys") team of [[Mercurio (wrestler)|Mercurio]], [[Pequeño Nitro]], [[Pequeño Olimpico]], [[Pequeño Violencia]] and [[Pierrothito]]. In the end Pequeño Olimpico pinned Mascarita Dorada to become the official challenger for [[Bam Bam (wrestler)|Bam Bam]]'s championship.<ref name=Pequeno2011>{{cite web|url=http://superluchas.net/2011/02/07/arena-coliseo-resultados-6-de-febrero-2011-pequeno-olimpico-gana-torneo-cibernetico-y-enfrentaran-a-bam-bam-por-el-campeonato-mundial-mini/|title=Arena Coliseo (resultados 6 de febrero 2011) Pequeño Olímpico gana torneo cibernético y enfrentaran a Bam Bam por el campeonato mundial mini|date=February 7, 2011|accessdate=November 19, 2012|first=Alex|last=Ruiz Glez|work=SuperLuchas|language=Spanish}}</ref> The following week Pequeño Olimpico defeated Bam Bam to win the title.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://superluchas.net/2011/02/14/arena-mexico-resultados-13-de-febrero-pequeno-olimpico-nuevo-campeon-mundial-mini-del-cmll/|title=Arena México (resultados 13 de febrero) Pequeño Olímpico nuevo campeón mundial mini del CMLL|date=February 14, 2011|accessdate=February 14, 2011|author=Ruiz Glez, Alex|work=SuperLuchas|language=Spanish}}</ref>
