==Pequeños Reyes del Aire (2014)== {{Infobox wrestling event |name=''Pequeños Reyes del Aire'' (2014) |image=PequenoReyesdeAire2014.jpg |caption=Poster for the "3 Kings Days" show with the ''Pequeños Reyes del Aire'' tournament |promotion = [[Consejo Mundial de Lucha Libre]] |date=January 5, 2014 |attendance= |venue=[[Arena Mexico]] |city = [[Mexico City, Mexico]] |liveevent=Y |lastevent=''[[La Copa Junior#La Copa Junior Tournament (2014)|La Copa Junior]]'' (2014) |nextevent=[[Fantastica Mania 2014]] |event=''Pequeños Reyes del Aire'' |lastevent2=''[[#Pequeños Reyes del Aire (2013)|Pequeños Reyes del Aire]]'' (2013) |nextevent2=''[[#Pequeños Reyes del Aire (2015)|Pequeños Reyes del Aire]]'' (2015) }} CMLL held the 2014 version of the '''''Pequeños Reyes del Aire''''' tournament on January 5, 2014, in [[Arena Mexico]] in [[Mexico City, Mexico]]. The ninth annual tournament featured a total of 10 ''[[Mini-Estrella]]s'': [[Astral (wrestler)|Astral]], [[Demus 3:16]], [[Electrico (wrestler)|Eléctrico]], [[Mercurio (wrestler)|Mercurio]], [[Pequeño Nitro]], [[Pequeño Olímpico]], [[Pierrothito]], [[Shockercito]], [[Stukita]] and [[Último Dragóncito]]. The match came down to Astral and Eléctrico, both on the same team during the early portions of the match. In end Eléctrico landed badly on a dive to the outside onto Astral and hurt both himself and Astral. When Astral was unable to compete he was counted out and Eléctrico was declared the winner. The impact from the dive was so severe that both Astral and Eléctrico ended up having to go to the hospital after the match.<ref name=PRdA2014>{{cite web | url=http://www.mediotiempo.com/mas-deportes/lucha-libre/noticias/2014/01/06/accidentado-torneo-en-la-mexico-astral-y-electrico-al-hospital | title=Accidentado torneo en la México, Astral y Eléctrico al hospital | date=January 6, 2014 | accessdate=August 1, 2014 | author=Redaccion | work=MedioTiempo | language=Spanish}}</ref><ref name=FuegoPRdA2014>{{cite web | url=http://www.fuegoenelring.com/noticias_detalle.php?articles_id=3705 | title=ELÉCTRICO, REY DEL AIRE DEL 2014 | first=Gonzalo | last=López Peralta | work=Fuego en el Ring | language=Spanish}}</ref>
