==Pequeños Reyes del Aire (2015)== {{Infobox wrestling event |name=''Pequeños Reyes del Aire'' (2015) |image=PequenoReyesdeAire2015.jpg |caption=Official poster for the January 6, 2015 show |promotion = [[Consejo Mundial de Lucha Libre]] |date=January 6, 2015<ref name=PRdR2015/> |attendance= |venue=[[Arena Mexico]]<ref name=PRdR2015/> |city = [[Mexico City, Mexico]]<ref name=PRdR2015/> |liveevent=Y |lastevent=''[[Infierno en el Ring (2014)|Infierno en el Ring]]'' (2014) |nextevent=[[Fantastica Mania 2015]] |event=''Pequeños Reyes del Aire'' |lastevent2=''[[#Pequeños Reyes del Aire (2014)|Pequeños Reyes del Aire]]'' (2014) |nextevent2=TBA }} The 2015 '''''Pequeños Reyes del Aire''''' (Spanish for "Little Kings of the Air") tournament was the tenth version of an annual [[professional wrestling]] tournament held by Mexican ''[[lucha libre]]'' promotion [[Consejo Mundial de Lucha Libre]] (CMLL) that started in 2007. The tournament is exclusively for competitors in CMLL's ''[[Mini-Estrella]]s'' division and is their version of the regular division's ''[[CMLL Reyes del Aire|Reyes del Aire]]'' tournament and has the same multi-man ''[[torneo cibernetico]]'' elimination format. The 2015 version of the tournament saw five ''[[Face (professional wrestling)|tecnicos]]'' (wrestling term for the "good guys") face off against five ''[[Heel (professional wrestling)|rudos]]'' (the "bad guys") wrestling until only one man remains in the ring. The ''tecnico'' team of [[Astral (wrestler)|Astral]], [[Electrico (wrestler)|Eléctrico]], [[Fantasy (Mini-Estrella)|Fantasy]], [[Shockercito]] and [[Último Dragoncito]] took on the ''rudo'' team of [[Pequeño Damián 666|Demus 3:16]], [[Mercurio (wrestler)|Mercurio]], [[Pequeño Nitro]], [[Pequeño Olímpico]] and [[Pierrothito]]. In the end Shockercito pinned Pierrothito to win the 2015 ''Pequeños Reyes del Aire'' tournament, the first tournament win of Shockercito's career.<ref name=PRdR2015>{{cite web | url=http://deportes.terra.com.mx/luchas/volador-jr-supera-en-mano-a-mano-a-rey-bucanero-en-el-cmll,f7170f297e1ca410VgnCLD200000b1bf46d0RCRD.html | title=Volador Jr. supera en mano a mano a Rey Bucanero en el CMLL | date=January 6, 2015 | accessdate=January 7, 2015 | work=Terra México | language=Spanish}}</ref>
